---
title: Warm Mexican-Style Bean Bowls with Tangy Guacamole
description: You'll never look at black beans the same way again after you've tasted this zesty, aromatic spin on a Mexican classic! We're sharing all the tricks to maximizing bean bowl flavour – from using both the zest and juice of fresh lime to our handy Enchilada Spice Blend. Even the rice gets a boost with fresh cilantro, while our fuss-free guacamole is the perfect tanging topping.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bols-de-haricots-a-la-mexicaine-207b6f73.jpg
